def_cn: 有待宣布，有待通知(书面通知用语)
def_en: tba is sometimes written in announcements to indicate that something such as the place where something will happen or the people who will take part is not yet known and will be announced at a later date. tba is an abbreviation for (缩略=) 'to be announced'.
